PrecisOrder which authorizes: (a) the grant of a Licence of Occupation to the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES POWER CORPORATION, for a term of ten (10) years, across a strip of land situate in WOOD BUFFALO NATIONAL PARK which is presently occupied by an electrical power transmission line; and (b) after the completion of a survey, to subsequently grant a forty-two (42) year lease over the same right-of-way.
